SELECT ?player ?height ?name WHERE {
  ?player a dbo:BasketballPlayer .
  ?player dbo:team ?team .
  ?team rdf:type dbo:BasketballTeam .
  ?team rdfs:label ?team_label .
  ?player dbo:height ?height .
  ?player foaf:name ?name
  FILTER (LANGMATCHES(LANG(?team_label), "EN"))
  FILTER STRSTARTS(?team_label, "NBA")
}
ORDER BY ?height
LIMIT 1
